description: I heard about a nice lido on the outskirts of Prague and decided to go there. I expected to find a lot of people swimming and sunbathing in this hot weather. Unfortunately, my phone navigation guided me to a disgusting pond instead. There was no chance that anyone would ever enter this green stinking water. Only person there was a young man observing fish swimming under the surface. We started talking and I immediately got aroused by this guy. He looked like a doll, cute and innocent. At least at the first glance. All I had to do was to show him money and he revealed his true self. Slutty and greedy was this dude. I took him behind nearby trees and absolutely rammed his beautiful ass. Not sure if he enjoyed it very much but I didn't care. Sweet guys like this aren't meant to be fucked gently.
title: Czech Hunter 472
